channel.title: 317 Delta
channel.description:
So this has never been a problem before until now..i got a new source and client and wanted to add an npc model and new item models..I added them correctly but they are invisible on my server.
They do show there names and I can click on them and equip the items..and the npc is on the map, but i cant see anything?
Anyone know why?
No using ::add model or any of the sort of commands work.

item.description:
@xneonx wrote:

Try going to your client files and open up your client class and search for models() then you might find something like if(s.startsWith("all models")) { models(); } Then just log in on your server and type in “all models” by itself.
